decks.notes: This deck is a control deck centered around the commander Varina, Lich Queen. The main goal is to maintain control of the game by utilizing a variety of spells and abilities. The deck includes a mix of removal spells such as Dismember, Eliminate, and Fatal Push, as well as countermagic like Force of Will and Counterspell. It also features powerful planeswalkers like Jace, the Mind Sculptor and Teferi, Hero of Dominaria. The deck's strategy is to control the board and disrupt opponents' plans through various removal, counter spells, and card advantage engines. It also takes advantage of powerful creatures like True-Name Nemesis and Brazen Borrower to further assert board dominance.

The core strategy of this deck is to control the game through a combination of counterspells, removal spells, and disruptive enchantments. Aminatou, the Fateshifter serves as the commander, providing card selection and manipulation to ensure the right answers are available at the right time. The deck includes a wide range of removal spells such as Fatal Push, Swords to Plowshares, and Vindicate to deal with threats efficiently. Counterspells like Force of Will and Mana Leak help disrupt opponent's game plan while cards like Thoughtseize and Inquisition of Kozilek allow for hand disruption. The goal is to outvalue and outmaneuver opponents by controlling the board and winning through incremental advantage.
